---
let { killerTitle } = Astro.props;
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../src/styles/styles.css" />
        <title>DBD Guide | {killerTitle}</title>
	</head>
    
	<body>
		<header>
			<h1>{killerTitle}</h1>
            <hr>
		</header>
		<main>
			<h2>General</h2>
                <img class='killer-portrait' src="../src/assets/mastermind_portrait.png" alt="{killerTitle}'s Character Portrait"/>
                <slot name='killer-description'/>
            <hr>

            <h2>Power</h2>
                <img class='power-icon' src="../src/assets/mastermind_power_icon.png" alt="{killerTitle}'s Power Icon"/>
                <slot name="power-description"/>
            <hr>

            <h2>Perks</h2>
                <p>{killerTitle} comes with 3 unique perks:</p>
                <img class='perk-icon' src="../src/assets/IconPerks_awakenedAwareness.png" alt="Awakened Awareness Perk Icon"/>
                <h3>Awakened Awareness</h3>
                    <p>While carrying a survivor, the auras of nearby survivors are revealed to you.</p>
                <img class='perk-icon' src="../src/assets/IconPerks_superiorAnatomy.png" alt="Superior Anatomy Perk Icon"/>
                <h3>Superior Anatomy</h3>
                    <p>When a survivor performs a fast vault near you, your vault speed is increased.</p>
                <img class='perk-icon' src="../src/assets/IconPerks_terminus.png" alt="Terminus Perk Icon"/>
                <h3>Terminus</h3>
                    <p>Once the Exit Gates are powered, all survivors suffer from the <dfn>Broken</dfn> status effect
                    until the gates are opened, at which point the effects linger for an additional 20 seconds.
                    The <dfn>Broken</dfn> status effect prevents survivors from healing themselves or others.</p>
            <hr>

            <h2>Playstyle Tips</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Use your power to quickly close the distance between you and survivors.</li>
                <li>Focus on hitting survivors with your power to build up their Infection Meter.</li>
                <li>Don't try to use your powers on short loops! You cannot turn while using your power.</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>For more advanced killer players, learning Wesker's Hug Tech is a great way to circumvent this.</li>
                </ul>
            </ul>
		</main>
		<footer>
			<nav> 
                <h2>Navigation</h2>
				<ul>
                    <li><a href="../index">Back to Home</a></li>
					<li><a href="./characters/mastermind">The Mastermind</a></li>
					<li><a href="./characters/singularity">The Singularity</a></li>
					<li><a href="./characters/unknown">The Unknown</a></li>
				</ul>
			</nav>

		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
